{"tid":1422764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟離地中產點睇勇武抗爭、不合作運動","createTime":"2019-08-06T11:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T13:17:28.000Z","uid":293844,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a0524ed32c7befff0fff8de195566d345f216b41","tid":1422764,"uid":293844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:55:03.000Z","msg":"琴晚同班離地中產親戚食飯，發覺<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要唔直接搞到佢地，出面放核彈佢地都唔理</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我班親戚大部分淺藍，有幾個淺黃和理非。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋對地鐵不合作運動最反感，不斷鬧啲人阻人搵食。但係佢哋對佔路無乜反應，我估係因為佢地睇唔到直接影響，只會以為塞車。<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以我贊成暫停一下地鐡不合作運動</span>。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋對義士攻狗屋、政總無反感。佢哋睇新聞直播就當係睇戲咁，仲不時評論啲義士同狗嘅表現。有啲人仲笑9黃大仙啲狗廢，連自己屋企都保唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋有啲抗拒魔法師，驚啲火會散開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議大家繼續夢遊參觀各區名勝，但係避免搞9啲返工返到上癮嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d3b0986fd795ea6a0ffc31cd6a874a73827bf0","tid":1422764,"uid":293844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:56:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"89e56b617a50f35ffbdc9815c9c7109b06773cab","tid":1422764,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"係連登搵中產？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b9be891e16b9fccf92ce1408422c88692d3339","tid":1422764,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f58c0b776539a3dc335f943756418691551ea54c","tid":1422764,"uid":293844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89e56b617a50f35ffbdc9815c9c7109b06773cab","tid":1422764,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"係連登搵中產？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:19:13.000Z","msg":"啲auntie uncle中產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3938417f02d04519c1019cdb61dbee21af18ff88","tid":1422764,"uid":273716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"不合作運動時要客氣啲<br />\n一啖砂糖一啖屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047e501012cf56f571b417994e669fa3b1bc5826","tid":1422764,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"不合佢阻返工真係好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e273a0de4b6e36b2f22f21ad99c6036b05d5670","tid":1422764,"uid":273716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:22:00.000Z","msg":"仲有落區時對街坊友善啲客氣啲<br />\n唔係有事點叫佢地撐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHit and run, and be humble!"},{"pid":"eac130721cb1cd8c082f55ecf2ac24c19b4250f1","tid":1422764,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}